            </title>
            <description>
                <![CDATA[<div class="tougao-user">感謝 IT 之家網友 <a href="https://m.ithome.com/html/app/open.html?url=ithome%3A%2F%2Fuserpage%3Fid%3D136010" rel="nofollow">Anonym0us</a>、<a href="https://m.ithome.com/html/app/open.html?url=ithome%3A%2F%2Fuserpage%3Fid%3D814573" rel="nofollow">嘣噔個嘣噔呦</a>、<a href="https://m.ithome.com/html/app/open.html?url=ithome%3A%2F%2Fuserpage%3Fid%3D55806" rel="nofollow">Zune</a> 的線索投遞！</div><p data-vmark="bd51"><a class="s_tag" href="https://www.ithome.com/" target="_blank">IT 之家</a> 3 月 4 日消息，備受關注的 M3 芯片版 MacBook Air 今晚悄然上線，與其一同到來的還有&nbsp;<a class="s_tag" href="https://iphone.ithome.com/" target="_blank">iPhone</a>15 手機殼、Apple Watch 錶帶<a target="_blank" href="https://apple.pvxt.net/c/1255290/435400/7639?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.apple.com.cn%2Fshop%2Faccessories%2Fall">新配色</a>等等。</p><p data-vmark="6112" style="text-align: center;"><img src="https://img.ithome.com/newsuploadfiles/2024/3/56f4115c-12a2-4d57-a519-17b238c2cf97.jpg?x-bce-process=image/format,f_auto" w="1440" h="810" title="蘋果 iPhone 15 手機殼、Apple Watch 錶帶推出多款全新配色" width="1440" height="461" referrerpolicy="no-referrer"></p><p data-vmark="c506"><a class="s_tag" href="https://iphone.ithome.com/" target="_blank">iPhone 15</a> 專用 MagSafe 硅膠保護殼新增淡薄荷色、豔陽色、淺藍色等，<span class="accentTextColor">售價為 399 元</span>。</p><p data-vmark="b001">據介紹，這款保護殼外部採用硅膠材質，內部則採用超細纖維製成的柔軟內襯。保護殼內置磁體，可與 iPhone&nbsp;15 精準對齊，充電時也不用取下，只要將 iPhone 吸附上 MagSafe 充電器，或放在 Qi 認證充電器上即可。</p><p style="text-align: center;" data-vmark="8127"><img src="https://img.ithome.com/newsuploadfiles/2024/3/be1be702-346f-4b69-8dfe-6cbe5da95ee4.png?x-bce-process=image/format,f_auto" w="1177" h="487" title="蘋果 iPhone 15 手機殼、Apple Watch 錶帶推出多款全新配色" width="1177" height="339" referrerpolicy="no-referrer"></p><p data-vmark="53e3">IT 之家注意到，Apple Watch 運動型錶帶同樣帶來豔陽色、淡薄荷色、淺藍色等配色，售價 379 元；迴環式運動錶帶帶來淡薄荷色、海洋藍色，售價 379 元；編織單圈錶帶帶來樹莓色、豔陽色、淺藍色，售價 779 元。</p><p style="text-align: center;" data-vmark="58f7"><img src="https://img.ithome.com/newsuploadfiles/2024/